    <title type="text">The new Classics for All Book Reviews site</title>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a
      href="http://www.theclassicslibrary.com/the-new-classics-for-all-book-reviews-site/">The new
      Classics for All Book Reviews site</a><br /><section class="post-meta fix
      post-nothumb media"><section class="bd post-header fix"><section class="bd
      post-title-section fix"><hgroup class="post-title fix"></hgroup><div
      class="metabar"><div class="metabar-pad"><em>By <span class="author vcard
      sc"><span class="fn"><a
      href="http://www.theclassicslibrary.com/author/stephenjenkin/" rel="author" title="Posts by
      Stephen Jenkin">Stephen Jenkin</a></span></span> On <time class="date
      time published updated sc" datetime="2015-03-24T10:26:40+00:00">March 24, 2015</time>
      · <span class="post-comments sc"><a
      href="http://www.theclassicslibrary.com/the-new-classics-for-all-book-reviews-site/#wp-comments"><span
      class="fb_comments_count">0</span> Comments</a></span>
      </em></div></div></section> </section></section><div
      class="fb-social-plugin fb-like fb_iframe_widget"
      data-href="http://www.theclassicslibrary.com/the-new-classics-for-all-book-reviews-site/"
      data-ref="above-post" data-width="450"><span style="height: 25px; vertical-align: bottom;
      width: 450px;"></span></div><blockquote class="tr_bq"><span
      style="font-size: x-small;">Following the recent merger of the Joint Association of
      Classical Teachers (JACT) with the Classical Association (CA) [hyperlink to <a
      href="http://www.classicalassociation.org/">www.classicalassociation.org</a>],
      Classics for All is delighted to say that the editors of JACT’s original <em>Journal of
      Classics Teaching&nbsp;</em> (Alan Beale and Dr Peter Jones) will now be editing
      under the CfA banner a wide range of concise reviews of books about the ancient world, designed
      to appeal both to teachers and the interested classical public alike.</span><br
      /><br /> <span style="font-size: x-small;">Go to <a
      href="http://www.classicsforall.org.uk/news/"
      target="_blank">http://www.classicsforall.org.uk/news/</a> for the location of the new
      site, which will be updated as new reviews come in.</span><br /><br />
      <span style="font-size: x-small;">The editors are always keen to add to their list of
      reviewers. Please contact either:</span><br /><span style="font-size:
      x-small;"><br />Alan Beale <a href="mailto:a.beale664@btinternet.com"
      target="_blank">a.beale664@btinternet.com</a><br />or<br />Peter Jones
      <a href="mailto:pvjones@friends-classics.demon.co.uk"
      target="_blank">pvjones@friends-classics.demon.co.uk</a></span><br
      /><br /> <span style="font-size: x-small;">If you have already reviewed for JACT
      and wish to continue but have <span style="text-decoration: underline;">not yet heard
      from us</span> about this new site, please email us. We may have lost your email address
      or it may be out of date.</span></blockquote>]]></content>
